Text: Hey Steve, it’s Meredith over at Beasley.(I just called). I’m with my Director building your proposal and I had a couple questions. Can you give me a jingle if you’re free please?
Meredith, Steve here from Solar first. Do we have the meeting scheduled for us all to convene?
Hi Steve! You were on my email list today! No not yet, what day and time would work for everyone?
Let me check. Any days you’re aiming for ? End of this week or next?
Can we aim for Friday?
Sure thing! Let me double check my colleagues calendar. What time are you thinking?
How late can you do Friday afternoon?
Let me check with my director this morning in our meeting.
I want her to join us
Unfortunately I forgot I have a dr appt on Friday afternoon at 3:30. Can we shoot for tomorrow or Monday? Apologies.
Monday
Perfect! Morning or afternoon?
Afternoon
We could both do 3 or 3:30pm Monday
330 please
Send invite to just me and I’ll forward
Thank you
Sorry I’m having teams issue
Re authenticating
Ok
Want me to resend the link?
I’m close
Hi Steve, it’s Meredith I wanted to check in with you and see if you had a chance to talk with everyone yet? Can we get a time on the schedule for after the Thanksgiving holiday?
Yes please. We had to fire our director of marketing. We have paused digital. A mess of two weeks
Thanks for patience
Oh no!!!! I’m so sorry! Ok I’ll connect with you in 2 weeks after thanksgiving to regroup and see where y’all are.
Hi Steve, it’s Meredith. I just sent you an email from a new email address. I hope you are having a happy holidays!

Hi Meredith, I resigned from my position right before the holidays. It wasn't pretty behind the scenes for me and I got out before it got ugly. Good company just not for me. Sadly, they aren't going to be a good lead for you without me there. They wanted to do everything in house but struggle to justify spend. I wanted to go fast. They want very careful planning and expectation forecasting

Ah! Gotcha. No worries. I sort of did same thing lol. I went back to my old agency because the one I was with ruined campaigns for clients that were running perfectly before I moved them over. I had to get out quickly as well. What are you up to now?

I haven't completely decided what is next. Taking some time in to January, maybe February to determine what's next. I am battling non compete language so I may have to shift from the industry depending on outcomes
But I'm open
Ouch! I’m so sorry
